   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-a" mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>Master...it's been a long while.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia${action:Talk}<BR>Oh, look who's here?<BR>Could this really be my long-lost disciple?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-b" mid="9"><![CDATA[<html> Hehehe… </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>I recall sending one of my disciples on an errand. A disciple who looks just like YOU! It was just ONE SIMPLE TASK, which till this day remains uncompleted. That was over FIVE YEARS AGO. ARE YOU THAT DISCIPLE? </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-c" mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>Are you laughing now? Is this all a big JOKE to you?<BR>You ignored your duties as a sorceress, and instead spent all that time on gambling all your gold away. What's more, you didn't come back here because you repented, but to run away from the people trying to collect the debts you owe! I'm utterly disappointed in you. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-c" image="QN_Npc_Karakule_silhouette.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-d" mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>I shouldn't have given you so much attention. I thought that under my guidance you would mature, and we could focus on your gifted talents as a sorceress. To think that I even considered you as a successor to <FONT color=#a82424>Master Karacule</FONT>! How wrong I was!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-e" mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>Yes? But I just returned. Would you mind if I take a break?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>Now you come crawling back to this place. Such insolence. Ugh, enough playing around. It appears that the blasted clerics have lost something important. Prove yourself to be not completely useless. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-e" image="QN_SoceressCynthia.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-f" mid="148"><![CDATA[<html>Going right away!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="147"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>Aww… You must be tired after your long journey.<BR>Well wait ... let me help you <FONT color=#a82424>rest in peace</FONT>.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Cynthia pulls out her staff.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1-f" image="QN_SoceressTara.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2" mid="135"><![CDATA[<html>Yes! I'm going!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>Listen to <FONT color=#a82424>Sorceress Tara</FONT> for details.<BR>And remember, this is your final chance. DO NOT fail me!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n015_sorceress_tara-1" image="QN_SoceressCynthia.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="121"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Tara${action:Talk}<BR>Are you lost?<BR>Is this your first time in this town? I think you should go and meet <FONT color=#a82424>Cynthia</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2" image="QN_SoceressTara.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2-b" mid="136"><![CDATA[<html>Master, I need some adaptation training.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2-a" mid="137"><![CDATA[<html>Fine, I'm going!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia${action:Talk}<BR>Why have you not gone to <FONT color=#a82424>Sorceress Tara</FONT> yet?<BR>You got something to say?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2-f" mid="149"><![CDATA[<html>(Hmm, at least you could spare me a little money ...)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="138"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>If you need a training, come to me to take the <FONT color=#a82424>Tutorial</FONT> about basic controls.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2-party" mid="140"><![CDATA[<html>Yeah, that sounds pretty good.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2-c" mid="141"><![CDATA[<html>I was trying to be nice...for once!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="139"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>Trying to be hardworking? YOU? Yeah, right!<BR>Anyway, the <FONT color=#a82424>Tutorial</FONT> teaches you all the basics you need to know. Do you want to take it?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-2-f" mid="150"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, Master!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="142"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>It seems that you haven't improved at all, even after five years. Should you want to take it later, come back and beg for it.<BR>(Select <FONT color=#a82424>Receive Tutorial</FONT>.)<BR>Is that clear?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
